<i>noun</i>: 호전 [호ː전], 향상 [향ː상], 차도 [차도], 제고 [제고], 전진 [전진], 상향 [상ː향], 발전상 [발쩐상], 개선 [개ː선], 개량화 [개ː량화], 개량 [개ː량] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호전 [호ː전]</dt><br>
<dd>1. improvement; getting better</dd><br>
<dd>일의 형편이나 상황이 좋은 방향으로 바뀜.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which things or a situation take a turn for the better.</dd><br>
<dd>2. improvement; getting better</dd><br>
<dd>병의 증세가 나아짐.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which the symptoms of a disease grow better.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>향상 [향ː상]</dt><br>
<dd>improvement; enhancement; progress</dd><br>
<dd>실력, 수준, 기술 등이 더 나아짐. 또는 나아지게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which an ability, level, skill, etc., gets better; or an act of making such a thing get better.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>차도 [차도]</dt><br>
<dd>improvement</dd><br>
<dd>병이 조금씩 나아지는 정도.</dd><br>
<dd>The degree of improvement in one's illness.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>제고 [제고]</dt><br>
<dd>enhancement; improvement</dd><br>
<dd>정도를 높임.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of raising the degree.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>전진 [전진]</dt><br>
<dd>1. moving forward</dd><br>
<dd>움직여서 앞으로 나아감.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of moving in a forward direction.</dd><br>
<dd>2. improvement; advances</dd><br>
<dd>정도나 수준 등이 발전하여 나아감.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of a degree, level, etc., improving and progressing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>상향 [상ː향]</dt><br>
<dd>1. being upward</dd><br>
<dd>위쪽을 향함. 또는 위쪽.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of facing upward, or the upper part.</dd><br>
<dd>2. increase; elevation</dd><br>
<dd>수치, 한도, 기준 등을 높임.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of increasing a figure, limit, standard, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>3. improvement</dd><br>
<dd>상태나 정도 등이 좋아져 감.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a status or degree, etc., gets better.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>발전상 [발쩐상]</dt><br>
<dd>improvement; development</dd><br>
<dd>발전한 모습.</dd><br>
<dd>The state or status of something having made progress or achieved development.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>개선 [개ː선]</dt><br>
<dd>improvement</dd><br>
<dd>부족한 점, 잘못된 점, 나쁜 점 등을 고쳐서 더 좋아지게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of reforming shortcomings, wrong or bad sides to character and making them better.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>개량화 [개ː량화]</dt><br>
<dd>improvement</dd><br>
<dd>새롭게 고치어 더 좋게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>Revising something to make it better.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>개량 [개ː량]</dt><br>
<dd>improvement</dd><br>
<dd>질이나 기능의 나쁜 점을 보완하여 더 좋게 고침.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of making up for shortfalls in quality or function and revise to be better.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>